**ProctoGuard** is a secure, AI-assisted online examination platform built for modern digital assessments. Designed to maintain academic integrity, the system provides intelligent proctoring, real-time monitoring, advanced analytics, customizable exam controls, and student performance insightsâ€”everything required for professional-grade online examinations.

