# â­ **Full Professional Description (Can be used in submission/GitHub/Resume)**

**ProctoGuard is a full-stack web-based proctored examination system built using Flask, SQLAlchemy, and modern JavaScript. It combines secure exam delivery with intelligent monitoring, ensuring fairness and transparency while giving faculty powerful tools for assessment and insights.**

### ğŸ” Proctoring & Anti-Cheating

* Tab-switch monitoring
* Activity logs with timestamps
* Suspicious behavior detection
* Randomized questions + shuffled options
* Unique question order per student

